text: Ðis sindan þa festermen Elfricas, Ulfcetel, cyninges reue, ond Merleswuain, Wulstain, Ulf, Ligolf, Barað, Farðain greua, ond Ascetel, Osulf ond Wulfeh, Folcric ond Elfred, Wegga and Aldsceorl, Gamal presbyter, Grim ond Grimcetel, Asmund ros, Grimcetel in Barnabi.

Godwina, Folc, Berhðor, Bretecol ond Arðolf, and Forna, Menning ond Wulger, þor in Ca ond Arcetel, Siuerð, Rauan, Arn, Colbrand ce, Blih, Eluwine<../images/lbar.gif>Snel, Godwine, Lef, Eðastan, Ulf, Elnod fre, Roscetel ond Edric, Grimcetel Haw, Ascetel, Grim in Cir.
Cetel presbyter, Gunner, Alfcetel in Ha, Ioluarð in Burhtun, Ulfcetel presbyter, Alfcetel ond Asmund, Leofnoð in Broðortun, þorcetel Unbainasuna, Ulf presbyter, þirne beorn, ond Ailaf in Braiþatun.
Wulfric ond Iustan, Rot in Hillum ond Grimcetel his mah, Raganald Asbeornnas suna, Ord ru proh in Bærnabi, Halwærð sæfugala suna, ond Arþor, <ldolf> presbyter, Auðcetel presbyter.
